From Robert Wade Subject Re Saturn Extended Warranty In article I We are Gaia writes In article Vivek Chickermane writes ADVICE on SATURN EXTENDED WARRANTY I placed an order for a Saturn and it is expected next The Saturn retailer gave me some pamphlets about the extended warranty plan and I have been thinking about Being a first time new car buyer I am seeking advice from veterans those who have bought Saturns FYI I have listed some of the features of the Saturn extended warranty The car comes with a years mile bumper to bumper Plan I Extended Powertrain Coverage Covers the cost of repairs to Engine Transaxle Front wheel drive hour roadside assistance program Coverage Term years miles Deductible i say extended warranties are a ripoff high profit item for but what i really want to point out here is that you are not buying you get free so what you are buying is keep that in mind when you look at the cost another point is that many car companies routinely fix car problems that are out of design manufacturing defects that the company owns up to keeping customer happy